ury.
During [[World War I]], ''Priarial'' collided with the British [[Steamship|steamer]]{{SS|Tropic||2}} in the [[English Channel]] off [[Le Havre]], [[France]], and sank with the loss of nineteen of her 26 crew.<ref name=French>{{cite web|url=http://www.naval-history.net/WW1NavyFrench.htm |title=French Navy |publisher=Naval History |accessdate=21 February 2013}}</ref>
